name: Timesheet Reminder
metaModel.name: TimesheetReminder
subject: Provide details for timesheet
content:
Hi $TimesheetReminder.employee.name$,


Please provide full details asap, please see below missing information.

$TimesheetReminder.timesheetReminderLineList : { it |

On week from $it.fromDate;format="dd-MM-yyyy"$ to $it.toDate; format="dd-MM-yyyy"$, you declared $it.workHour$ hours while you should declare $it.requiredHours$ hours.

}$

please correct urgently your timesheet
